torage-1851528900\"\u003edestined for an all-digital future\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, but even as players overwhelmingly buy games digitally, they still appear to be opting for consoles with disc drives over ones without them. According to recent data on the current state of the console race, digital-only PlayStation 5s appear to be the least popular hardware this generation. - Ethan Gach \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/ps5-5-pro-disc-physical-xbox-series-x-s-sales-digital-1851679873\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/ps5-5-pro-disc-physical-xbox-series-x-s-sales-digital-1851679873\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7\" data-recommend-id=\"image://bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of a Black Ops 6 trailer showing a horde of zombies on the Terminus map.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of a Black Ops 6 trailer showing a horde of zombies on the Terminus map.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A screenshot of a Black Ops 6 trailer showing a horde of zombies on the Terminus map.\" data-chomp-id=\"bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of a Black Ops 6 trailer showing a horde of zombies on the Terminus map.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Treyarch / Activision\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7\" data-recommend-id=\"image://bb2b3e473a7ed75d2b6632d756d43fb7\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of a Black Ops 6 trailer showing a horde of zombies on the Terminus map.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eEarlier this week, I felt a feeling I hadn’t felt in a long while: I was looking forward to the release of a \u003cem\u003eCall of Duty \u003c/em\u003egame. \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-direct-everything-we-know-1851531121\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-direct-everything-we-know-1851531121\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eBlack Ops 6\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, the latest installment in the long-running \u003cem\u003eCall of Duty \u003c/em\u003esub-series, has spent the last several months hyping up audiences about all of its changes and innovations, like \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-multiplayer-beta-weekend-1851638800\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-multiplayer-beta-weekend-1851638800\"\u003eits quickened pace and omnimovement\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. Meanwhile, the promotional tour has \u003cem\u003ealso \u003c/em\u003ebeen deliberately trying to harken back to some kind of golden age for the franchise, which seems as embattled as ever despite still regularly posting huge numbers and breaking records year after year. In recent weeks, players have been excited over the return of systems like prestige, which I didn’t even realize had been stripped from the games, but my personal favorite bit of messaging has been around Zombies, a fan-favorite cooperative mode that has become a staple of \u003cem\u003eCoD \u003c/em\u003esince it was first introduced in 2008. - Moises Taveras \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-zombies-impressions-xbox-1851681562?_gl=1*1czq0jo*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTcyOTk1ODI2MC4zMy4wLjE3Mjk5NTgyODguMzIuMC4w\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-zombies-impressions-xbox-1851681562?_gl=1*1czq0jo*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTcyOTk1ODI2MC4zMy4wLjE3Mjk5NTgyODguMzIuMC4w\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
